{"tid":619853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今年香港天氣好怪","createTime":"2018-04-07T05:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T05:56:00.000Z","uid":2641,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"262e0e4ba52906e20c0be97887bc5013644308e2","tid":619853,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"早幾年呢個時候應該係好潮濕，濕到牆身都滴晒水咁，但今年我屋企連霉菌都唔係好見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有以前既4月九成時間都係好似夏天咁，但呢排好明顯冇以前既4月咁熱，即使26、27度都冇咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\n最後係溫差，以前日夜溫差可以話係冇，但呢排溫差係好明顯，可以去到5-6度，同一件衫日間出汗夜晚係會有d涼<br />\n<br />\n有冇氣候撚可以解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43f18f144013806319a2c421d871e80a69d88d1","tid":619853,"uid":143411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"前兩日好熱 琴日好凍"},{"pid":"c902adb3a1390355ca828b36dc9f03a11be81985","tid":619853,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfb885618dfc89babcd67b4880f815502cb503e6","tid":619853,"uid":69528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:19:43.000Z","msg":"大陸霧霾及污染物影響，完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33481096fbe408c8c13f2647a031c7730a28bd12","tid":619853,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d43f18f144013806319a2c421d871e80a69d88d1","tid":619853,"uid":143411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"前兩日好熱 琴日好凍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"啱呀，以前既4月點會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4779d6dc740acbef22a436f8b2056d9d1ca0e130","tid":619853,"uid":2641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:56:00.000Z","msg":"